<data>&lt;div class=b&gt;&lt;a href="/"&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/18It"&gt;18It Itivuttakapāḷi&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/18It/3"&gt;3 Tikanipāta&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/18It/3/3.5"&gt;3.5 Pañcamavagga&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="i"&gt;3.5.7 Kāmayogasutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Tikanipāta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Pañcamavagga&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Kāmayogasutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_685"&gt; &lt;div class="divNumber"&gt;96.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;685&lt;/span&gt;Vuttañhetaṃ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṃ—  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_686"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;686&lt;/span&gt;“Kāmayogayutto, bhikkhave, bhavayogayutto āgāmī hoti āgantā itthattaṃ. Kāmayogavisaṃyutto, bhikkhave, bhavayogayutto anāgāmī hoti anāgantā itthattaṃ. Kāmayogavisaṃyutto, bhikkhave, bhavayogavisaṃyutto arahā hoti, khīṇāsavo”ti. Etamatthaṃ bhagavā avoca. Tatthetaṃ iti vuccati—  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_687"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;687&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;“Kāmayogena saṃyuttā,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;bhavayogena cūbhayaṃ;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Sattā gacchanti saṃsāraṃ,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;jātimaraṇagāmino.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_688"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;688&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Ye ca kāme pahantvāna,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;appattā āsavakkhayaṃ;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Bhavayogena saṃyuttā,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;anāgāmīti vuccare.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_689"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;689&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Ye ca kho chinnasaṃsayā,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;khīṇamānapunabbhavā;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Te ve pāraṅgatā loke,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;ye pattā āsavakkhayan”ti.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_690"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;690&lt;/span&gt;Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="CENTER" id="p_18It_691"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;691&lt;/span&gt;Sattamaṃ.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="CENTER" id="p_18It_692"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;692&lt;/span&gt;Tatiyabhāṇavāraṃ.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="tn"&gt;&lt;div class=plcb&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="prevP()" id="prevL" name="268470" title="Go to previous page"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt; 3.5.6 Kāmūpapattisutta&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="upP()" id="upL" name="266891" title="Go to parent page"&gt;up&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="nextP()" id="nextL" name="268472" title="Go to next page"&gt;3.5.8 Kalyāṇasīlasutta &amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</data>
